==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Apace
<hw>A*pace"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>a-</ets> + <ets>pace</ets>. OE. <ets>a pas</ets> at a walk, in
which <ets>a</ets> is the article. See <er>Pace</er>.]</ety> <def>With a
quick pace; quick; fast; speedily.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His dewy locks did drop with brine <qex>apace</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A visible triumph of the gospel draws on <qex>apace</qex>.</q>
<rj><au>I. Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Apaches</ent>⟦br⟧
